      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEST FOR PACE (5) was a little disappointing last start at this track when 7th (30.59) over 510m. Has won here at this journey. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has ability and looks hard to stop. KING ETERNAL (1) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (24.09) in a Grade 4 at this track. Has the ability and expected to do much better. OUT THE BOTTLE (7) is a handy type who notched his 15th career success when too good (19.93) from Box 5 at Capalaba. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Expected to feature again. WINTER BALE (8) scored a sizzling Grade 4/5 win in 23.58 last time. Can measure up again.",
